line_1: Sun-beams sent down to prop one friar's staff,
line_2: And hell broke loose to make another laugh;

line_1: As Constable wou'd take his Staff:
The sudden whirl, stretch'd leg, and lifted staff,
line_2: Which please the vulgar, make the critic laugh.

line_1: Have laid aside the general's staff
line_2: And public cares, with you to laugh;
